WHEN USER GOES IDLE:
â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€

User Activity Stops
  â”‚ (no keyboard/mouse for 150 seconds)
  â”‚
  â–¼
Hypridle Detects Inactivity
  â”‚ timeout = 150 reached
  â”‚
  â–¼
Check: Is screen locked?
  â”‚ pidof hyprlock
  â”‚
  â”œâ”€ YES â†’ Skip screensaver (already locked)
  â””â”€ NO â†’ Run screensaver launcher
  
